casebody.data:
Doug JASTER and Elizabeth Jaster, Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
CITY OF GARBER, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1761 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

The City of Garber seeks reversal of the district court decision granting ownership rights over three adjoining sections of disputed puted property to Doug and Elizabeth Jaster. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
